    "He championed contemporary art at a time in the post-war years when other art historians were decrying contemporary art.": [],
    "He took on Vienna-school art historian (and his future Munich colleague) <a href=\"/sedlmayrh\">Hans Sedlmayr</a>, in 1950 in the celebrated debate of post-war intellectuals known as the \"Darmst\u00e4dter Gespr\u00e4ch.\"": [],
